                    <span class="fs-credits-bold">Production</span><br>
                    Spaces&Creatures - Guilherme Bullejos, Diego Spinola, Gabriela Veiga, Junior de Gois, Lina Lopes & Maurício Veiga
                    <br /><br />
                    
                    <span class="fs-credits-bold">Architecture</span><br>
                    Todos Arquitetura - Fabio Mota, Camila Escobar, Rogério Gurgel, Sandra Telles & Vinícius Fernandes
                    <br /><br />

                    <span class="fs-credits-bold">Modeling in collaboration with Pax</span><br>
                    Ana Carolina, Paula Sertório & Victor Paixão
                    <br /><br />

                    <span class="fs-credits-bold">Botanist</span><br>
                    Gabriela Veiga
                    <br /><br />
                    
