                    Zeromáquina - Ana Carolina, Paula Sertório & Victor Paixão
                    <br /><br />

                    <span class="fs-credits-bold">Prototyping space</span><br>
                    Lilo.Zone
                    <br /><br />
                    
                    <span class="fs-credits-bold">Photography and video</span><br>
                    Triangle Studio & Ricardo Bassetti

                    <br /><br /><br /><br />
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
